story.text: Met with local businessmen for breakfast and coffee. Very fruitful. Then made progress on the brief and joined the federated wiki weekly meeting.
Much of what they say is over my head, but nuggets of it are not - which is very exciting.
Need to work on New Shape and get a version to Ward et. al. for review.
